Package org.settings4j.connector.db.dao.hibernate

Class Summary
ConfigurationByteArray Extends the org.hibernate.cfg.Configuration ( Configuration) with one Methode to load a Hibernate Configuration-File from a ByteArray.
SettingsDAOHibernate The Hibernate Implementation of the SettingsDAO Interface
